title: Athletic Club 2 - 3 Barcelona - HIGHLIGHTS & GOALS - 1/6/2021
author: beIN SPORTS USA
description:
Two goals from Leo Messi and one from Pedri González gave FC Barcelona victory over Athletic Club in San Mamés, embittering Marcelino García Toral's debut on the rojiblanco bench.
